bronze.name: Lob
bronze.title: Lob provides a print and mail API that enables companies to send physical mail as easily as sending emails. Developers can use Lob to send transactional postcards, posters, letters, photos, checks, and greeting cards via an API.

bronze.name: Syncano
bronze.title: Syncano lets you easily build powerful apps. Integrate with any API, minimize boilerplate code and control your data - all from one place.

bronze.name: Treehouse
bronze.title: With Treehouse you can learn the valuable skills you need to go from zero coding experience to job ready for the tech industry. Start learning today!

bronze.name: Fedora
bronze.title: The Fedora Project is a partnership of free and open source software developers that builds Fedora, one of the leading open source Linux distributions available today.

silver.name: Praxis: Break the mold
silver.title: Praxis is a one year program for entrepreneurially young people that combines a job at an amazing company, intensive professional development, and self-guided education.
